Guardian of the Flame

Edit on GitHub

Overview

UnlockClear Freja's Memories (Chapter 2).
LocationFuego Mines (Chapter 2).
Title -
Description Normal dungeon with no restrictions.
Floors 22F Bosses 22F
Change Crystals 0F, 21F Checkpoints 10F
Max Level - Bring Buddy Yes
Bring In Items Yes Take Out Items Yes
Shops/Duels Yes Den of Monsters No
Reapers Yes Bookmark Yes
Unidentified Equipment, Consumables
Rewards 1. Black Mage's Memories (10F).
2. Can unlock Another White Mage's Memories.
After reaching 10F and checking the door.
3. Fire Apple (21F).
Chocobo's Max SP 3 4.
4. Dungeon added to Mirror of Memory.
5. Can unlock Meja's Memories.
6. Can unlock Stella's Memories.
7. Can unlock Harry's Memories.
8. Can unlock The Genius Inventor's Memories.
Must also clear Another White Mage's Memories.
